<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SFMC Youth Ministry — Move Wantem Faith</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Crimson+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --maroon: #6B0E23;
    --maroon-dark: #4a0918;
    --maroon-light: #8a1530;
    --gold: #C9963A;
    --gold-light: #e0b45a;
    --gold-pale: #f5e8cc;
    --cream: #fdf8f0;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --charcoal: #1a1a1a;
    --grey: #5a5a5a;
    --grey-light: #e8e4df;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    background: var(--maroon-dark);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 24px;
    height: 56px;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 28px;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    background: var(--maroon);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 80px 24px 72px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(201,150,58,0.18) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .hero h1 span { color: var(--gold); }
  .hero-verse {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 10px;
  }
  .hero-ref {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .hero-slogan {
    margin-top: 36px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* ── SECTION WRAPPER ── */
  .section {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 24px;
  }
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--maroon);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .divider {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  /* ── ABOUT / STATS ── */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--grey);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .about-text .closing-verse {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--maroon);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 12px 18px;
    margin-top: 28px;
    background: var(--gold-pale);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .stat-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey-light);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--maroon);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .stat-number {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--maroon);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--grey);
    margin-top: 6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── FOUR SQUARE ── */
  .foursquare-bg {
    background: var(--maroon);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .foursquare-bg .section-title { color: var(--white); }
  .foursquare-bg .section-label { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .four-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .four-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,150,58,0.35);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 28px 20px;
  }
  .four-card-icon {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .four-card-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .four-card-leaders {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .four-card-count {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .four-card-count span {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── EXECUTIVES ── */
  .exec-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .exec-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey-light);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .exec-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--maroon), var(--gold));
  }
  .exec-initial {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    background: var(--maroon);
    color: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .exec-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .exec-role {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--maroon);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── PROGRAMME / CALENDAR ── */
  .phase-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .phase-tab {
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--grey-light);
    background: transparent;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    color: var(--grey);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }
  .phase-tab:hover, .phase-tab.active {
    background: var(--maroon);
    border-color: var(--maroon);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .phase-tab.gold-tab.active {
    background: var(--gold);
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .month-block { margin-bottom: 48px; display: none; }
  .month-block.visible { display: block; }

  .month-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .month-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--maroon);
  }
  .month-theme {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .month-verse {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--grey);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .session-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .session-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey-light);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .session-row:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }
  .session-row.special {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    background: var(--gold-pale);
  }
  .session-date {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--grey);
  }
  .session-focus {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .session-badge {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .badge-exec { background: var(--maroon); color: var(--white); }
  .badge-speaker { background: var(--gold); color: var(--white); }
  .badge-devotion { background: #5b4b8a; color: var(--white); }
  .badge-education { background: #1a6b3a; color: var(--white); }
  .badge-recreation { background: #1a5480; color: var(--white); }
  .badge-service { background: #7a4010; color: var(--white); }
  .badge-special { background: var(--maroon-dark); color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid var(--gold); }

  .circuit-note {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--maroon);
    background: var(--gold-pale);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .session-main { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--charcoal); }
  .session-facilitator {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 3px;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  /* ── PHASE OVERVIEW ── */
  .phase-overview {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .phase-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey-light);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 20px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--maroon);
  }
  .phase-number {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .phase-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--maroon);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .phase-months {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--grey);
  }

  /* ── HIGHLIGHTS ── */
  .highlights-bg { background: #f5f0ea; }
  .highlights-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .highlight-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .highlight-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .highlight-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--maroon);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .highlight-text { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--grey); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* ── MEMBERS TABLE ── */
  .members-section { overflow-x: auto; }
  .members-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .members-table th {
    background: var(--maroon);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .members-table td {
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-light);
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .members-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: rgba(201,150,58,0.06); }
  .members-table tr:hover td { background: var(--gold-pale); }
  .group-dot {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 6px;
  }
  .dot-devotion { background: #5b4b8a; }
  .dot-education { background: #1a6b3a; }
  .dot-recreation { background: #1a5480; }
  .dot-service { background: #7a4010; }

  .filter-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .filter-btn {
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--grey-light);
    background: transparent;
    border-radius: 16px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--grey);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .filter-btn:hover, .filter-btn.active { color: var(--white); border-color: transparent; }
  .filter-btn.f-all.active { background: var(--maroon); }
  .filter-btn.f-devotion.active { background: #5b4b8a; }
  .filter-btn.f-education.active { background: #1a6b3a; }
  .filter-btn.f-recreation.active { background: #1a5480; }
  .filter-btn.f-service.active { background: #7a4010; }

  /* ── CONNECT ── */
  .connect-bg {
    background: var(--maroon-dark);
    color: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .connect-bg .section-title { color: var(--white); }
  .connect-bg .section-label { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .connect-bg .divider { background: var(--gold); margin: 16px auto 40px; }
  .connect-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .connect-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,150,58,0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .connect-card-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .connect-card-value {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .connect-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--maroon-dark);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 14px 36px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }
  .connect-btn:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ── ANNOUNCEMENTS ── */
  .announcements-bg { background: var(--cream); }
  .announcements-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .announcement-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey-light);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .announcement-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(107,14,35,0.08);
  }
  .announcement-card-top {
    background: var(--maroon);
    padding: 14px 18px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .announcement-date-badge {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .announcement-type-tag {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: rgba(201,150,58,0.18);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,150,58,0.35);
  }
  .announcement-body { padding: 18px; }
  .announcement-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--maroon);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .announcement-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--grey);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .announcement-empty {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 56px 24px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 2px dashed var(--grey-light);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .announcement-empty-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; opacity: 0.4; }
  .announcement-empty-text {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--grey);
  }
  .announcement-empty-text strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--maroon);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  footer span { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .four-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .exec-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .phase-overview { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .highlights-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .announcements-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .connect-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .session-row { grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; }
    .session-badge { display: none; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a class="nav-logo" href="#">SFMC Youth Ministry</a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#groups">Groups</a></li>
      <li><a href="#leaders">Leaders</a></li>
      <li><a href="#programme">Programme</a></li>
      <li><a href="#members">Members</a></li>
      <li><a href="#announcements">Announcements</a></li>
      <li><a href="#connect">Connect</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">Sister Fairhall Memorial United Church · Port Moresby, PNG</div>
  <h1>From <span>Listening</span><br>to <span>Leading</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-verse">"But don't just listen to God's word. You must do what it says."</p>
  <p class="hero-ref">James 1:22</p>
  <p class="hero-slogan">Move Wantem — Faith · 2026</p>
</section>


  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">Who We Are</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">A Ministry Rooted in Faith,<br>Built for the Next Generation</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>The SFMC Youth Ministry exists to involve and engage young people who attend Sister Fairhall Memorial United Church. We are the upcoming generation — the future leaders of this church — called to carry on what has been built before us.</p>
        <p>We help young people connect with their spirituality, deepen their understanding of God's word, and establish a strong foundation for a lifelong faith journey. We encourage active participation in the life of the church, fostering a sense of belonging and commitment among our youth.</p>
        <p>Our 2026 programme, <em>From Listening to Leading</em>, takes us through four phases of growth — from learning to hear God's voice, to walking by faith, to building character, to leading with influence.</p>
        <div class="closing-verse">
